{
  "name": "Intensified Weather",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/weather.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Choose Aridity, Cold, Heat, Precipitation, or Wind. The target suffers the effect of that weather at severity level 3. Precipitation of severity level 3 causes light rain, not fog. If you possess talents or feats that would increase the severity of that type of weather that you can create, apply that increase to the effects of this shroud. If the target is already in weather of the chosen type at the same severity or higher, it suffers the effect of the chosen type of weather as if it were one step more severe.</p>\n<p>This shroud counts as whichever type of weather you chose for the purpose of causing additional effects. You may apply this shroud multiple times to a single target, choosing a different type of weather each time.</p>\n",
